    <abstract>
      <t>It is hard to adjust traffic in a traditional IP network from time to time through manual configurations. It is desirable to have a mechanism for setting up routing policies, which adjusts traffic automatically. This document describes BGP Extensions for Routing Policy Distribution (BGP RPD) to support this with a controller.</t>
